[Student "S"]
{WEST bids 2\C as New Minor Forcing, hoping EAST has three \Hs.

EAST does not have three \Hs and he has no other bid to make that 
will describe his hand any better. He cannot bid Notrump again without a \C stopper. 
So EAST rebids the 5-card \D suit.

WEST has nowhere to go, so passes.}

